ADDITIONAL NOTICE — INTENTIONALLY VULNERABLE SOFTWARE

This repository contains deliberately insecure application code intended
solely for security training, research, and educational purposes.

- Do NOT deploy any of these labs to a publicly reachable host.
- Do NOT copy any of the vulnerable patterns into production software.
- Run each lab in an isolated container on a loopback-only interface.

The authors accept no responsibility for misuse of the code provided here.
